    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear that, but when you say the industry \"prioritizes rapid development over preemptive caution,\" it feels like you're suggesting they're being reckless. If we're talking about actual survival, is it even possible to have a \"balanced\" debate between these two, or is one side objectively more valid given the stakes?",
